pageProduct.name: U by Kotex Liners Nude 30 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

U by Kotex® Nude Liners are designed for Everyday Freshness. Breathable and unbelievably thin, you'll feel like you're wearing nothing at all. Don't forget, these 2 in 1 liners are perfect for both your favourite pair of undies or g-string.

  • Breathable backing: allows air to circulate so your skin breathes naturally
  • Convertible: Fold to 'convert' to G-string liner
  • Wafer-thin & super soft: Perfect for your favourite undies or G-string
  • Come in handy purse packs
  • Perfect for everyday freshness

 

Everyday Freshness

Boxed Contents: 30 Liners

Size: 30 Pack

Fits: Undies or G to string

Directions

Do not flush
